{"tid":604003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係我真心膠？還是連登仔做新聞？","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T09:38:54.000Z","uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5530d7aba91e45c3a24ed2ea8ce6cf93a423938a","tid":604003,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f24f991f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0527b018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次的士狗慢駛， 就話搞到救護車送唔切大肚婆入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次就話警察路祭， 搞到撞車呀婆送唔切入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係兩篇嘢個pattern一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都覺得個差佬係咎由自取， 而且不嬲都唔鍾意死黑警， 但係點都冇理由 作新聞詆毀警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n看客觀事實批評警察先係講道理， 如果鳩屈黑警， 咁我哋同班廢老藍絲有乜嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔肯定係作新聞還是諷刺黑警"}]}